1354382805707481089.Text: What happened yesterday?When I crossed barricades with youngsters, Nihangs crossed the barricades mounted on their horses, no one knew where to go. There was violence. Police fires tear gas and lathicarged. Some youngsters broke glasses of buses majority were trying to stop them

1354382816239353859.Text:
One man told that we have crossed ring road. there were reports of lathicharge. Some went back. We marched forward
not knowing where to go. Crossed some metro station. Some took turns to go towards ring road. Then someone said we are going to Red fort. I had tweeted about this.

1354382828922941441.Text: Then We marched but some boys said we are just 100 people what  would we do at Red fort. So they walked and took auto to go towards Burari side. From Burari, I took lifts from different people and then Marched forward.

1354382843955339265.Text: In middle of road saw Kanwar Grewal, signers and activists.  Leaders of Kisan Mazdoor Sangharsh committee were there. They had stopped and was addressing farmers where to go.

1354382850557140993.Text: By that Time I had received phone call from friends that they had reached red fort. So Instead of going towards ITO or stopping with farmers I took auto to Red fort.

1354382858283048962.Text: There was not even a single farmer leader at Red fort. Farmers and their Tractors were  their. I saw Nishan Sahib and people raising slogans. No one knew what to do. Everyone did whatever they could. Dance, sing and raise slogans.
